No matter what you're looking for, Temu has you covered, including fashion, home decor, handmade crafts, beauty & cosmetics, clothing, shoes, and more.












































Temu Brightness Adjuster allows you to easily adjust the brightness of the Temu website to suit your viewing preferences. With a simple and intuitive slider, you can increase or decrease the brightness directly from the extension’s popup window, providing a more comfortable browsing experience, especially in low light or high glare conditions.

Features:

Adjust Brightness: Use a convenient slider to control the brightness level of the Temu website.
Easy to Use: Access the slider directly from the extension’s popup; no complicated settings required.
Seamless Integration: The brightness adjustment is applied instantly to the page, ensuring a smooth and responsive experience.
Minimal Permissions: The extension only requests access to adjust brightness on the Temu website, keeping your browsing secure.
